+    //   - integer -> decimal text (CAST AS TEXT); e.g. 3 -> "3"
+    //   - real    -> decimal text (CAST AS TEXT); e.g. 3.5 -> "3.5"
+    //   - true    -> "true", false -> "false"  (preserve the JSON literal, NOT the
+    //                SQLite `1`/`0` that a bare `CAST(json_extract(...) AS TEXT)`
